                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Through the Straight Pass<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of Suffering</l>
                    <l>The Martyrs even trod - </l>
                    <l>Their feet opon Temptation - </l>
                    <l>Their<add type="alternate" extent="foreheads">faces</add>
 foreheads - opon God - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Stately - Shriven Company -</l>
                    <l>Convulsion playing round - </l>
                    <l>Harmless as Streaks of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Meteor - </l>
                    <l>Opon a Planet's Bond - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Their faith the Everlasting<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Troth - </l>
                    <l>Their Expectation -<add type="alternate" extent="sure -">fair -</add>
 sure -</l>
                    <l>The Needle to the North<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Degree </l>
                    <l>Wades so - through Polar<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Air - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
